description: Celebrating for 888 followers on twitter, “Aku Cinta Kamu : I Love You” became a tagline to my gratitude to all friends who always support my artwork. On the words that I didn't get to say to all of you one by one. Thanks to all the friends who have seen the journey of the process of making my artwork. Thank you for the good energy, knowledge, and friendship. i love you, you are all cool. Pure love, keep burn and making art!
